1. Added environment variable debugging information to help diagnose issues
2. Changed the error handling test to use real credentials but an invalid endpoint instead of fake credentials
3. Added more robust error logging to help diagnose test failures
4. Added checks for missing credentials before attempting tests
5. Used environment variables for OAuth redirect URI and scope values
