# Updates for Authentication Test Files

Based on the instruction to separate unit tests (with mocks) from true integration tests (with real API calls), I need to restructure the current test files. The file `auth-manager.integration.test.js` currently uses mocks, which contradicts best practices for integration testing.

## Files to Update:

1. Rename the current file to `auth-manager.test.js` since it uses mocks
2. Create a new true integration test file `auth-manager.integration.test.js`

## Changes for Each File:

### 1. Current file  `tests/auth/auth-manager.test.js`

This file will keep all the existing mock-based tests.

### 2. New file  `tests/auth/auth-manager.integration.test.js`

This will be a true integration test file that:
